          Where We Build
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Proudly serving communities throughout Ontario
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-4 text-center">
        <div class="p-4">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-2">üèûÔ∏è</div>
